## Interactive Dashboard
Built at [dashboard/](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/index.html) — 3 files ([index.html](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/index.html), [style.css](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/style.css), [app.js](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/app.js))

### Features
- **6 tabs**: Overview, Incident Analysis, KDSG Impact, Remediation, Public Advisory, OSINT & Coverage, Triage & Attack Chain
- **Threat Stream Ticker**: Live animated scrolling ticker with real-time OSINT updates at the top of the portal.
- **Dynamic Triage Calculator**: Interactive JS engine calculating risk score (0-100%) and outputting custom mitigation actions based on selected integrations.
- **Kill Chain Graph**: Visual node map detailing the Sterling Bank pivot into Remita's core infrastructure.
- Premium dark-mode with animated severity bars and pulsing threat indicators
- Interactive remediation checklist with localStorage persistence

